t was the name of the father of  Alexander the Great . It was also the name of one of Christ's apostles, of a deacon ordained by the apostles after the death of Christ, and of several other early saints.  See also  Philippa ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Philippe I de LEVIS was born in 1155, in Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France, his father, Bertrand De Levis, was 25 and his mother, Jourdaine De La Roche En Regnier, was 25. He had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Elisabeth de PALAISEAU. He died in 1203, at the age of 48, and was buried in Lèves, Eure-et-Loir, Centre, France."},"et":{"1155–1203":"1155–1203","1165–1210":"1165–1210","1180–1230":"1180–1230","–Female":"Surnud","1130–1180":"1130–1180","1130–Female":"1130–Surnud","1203":"1203","1155":"1155","1210":"1210","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","1130":"1130","1180":"1180","Leves, Departement d'Eure-et-Loir, Centre, France":"Lèves, Eure-et-Loir, Centre, Prantsusmaa","Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, France":"Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1155–1203":"1155–1203","1165–1210":"1165–1210","1180–1230":"1180–1230","–Female":"Kuollut","1130–1180":"1130–1180","1130–Female":"1130–Kuollut","1203":"1203","1155":"1155","1210":"1210","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","1130":"1130","1180":"1180","Leves, Departement d'Eure-et-Loir, Centre, France":"Lèves, Eure-et-Loir, Centre, Ranska","Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Lévis-Saint-Nom, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Ranska","Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, France":"Mirepoix, Ariège, Occitanie, Ranska"},"fr":{"1155–1203":"1155–1203","1165–1210":"1165–1210","1180–1230":"1180–1230","–Female":"Décédée","1130–1180":"1130–1180","1130–Female":"1130–Décédée","1203":"1203","1155":"1155","1210":"1210","1165":"1165","1230":"1230","1130":"1130","1180":"1180","Leves, Departement d'Eure-et-Loir, Centre, France":"Lèves, Eure-et-Loir, Centre, France","Lévis-Saint-No